com.thomsonreuters.upa.valueadd.domainrep.rdm.dictionary

Interface DictionaryRefresh

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DictionaryMsg, MsgBase

    public interface DictionaryRefresh
extends DictionaryMsg
    The RDM Dictionary Refresh. Used by an OMM Provider to provide the content of a Dictionary.
